import React from "react"; import propTypes from "prop-types" const Profile = ({username, tag, location, avatar, stats}) => { return (

{username}

@{tag}

{location}

  • Followers {stats.subs}
  • Views {stats.vievs}
  • Likes {stats.likes}
) } Profile.propTypes = { username: propTypes.string, tag: propTypes.string.isRequired, location: propTypes.string, avatar: propTypes.string.isRequired, stats: propTypes.shape({ likes: propTypes.number, subs: propTypes.number, views: propTypes.number }) } export default Profile
